@nksocialstudies @korytellers @NDSU I'll be honest...I was multi-tasking when I read this earlier, and that's actually what I thought this was. I wrote up some sort of WTH post, then had to delete it once I realized what it was saying.

I'm terrified to stand in the entry of my grandma's apartment tomorrow for her 92nd birthday party in case I infect her and she dies but I'm SUPER STOKED the @NDSU students in #fargo are partying like there isn't a global pandemic. 

Your selfishness extends beyond yourselves.

Just saw a @NDSU commercial ad on @hulu streaming platform. It showcased a variety of students. 

The variety that was noticeably absent, however, was Native American students or really, minorities in general. There was one black student. That's it. That's unacceptable
I'm bummed that @jamzread will not be reprising his role as Chase & Finn's dad on @GeneralHospital. I've been a big fan of his since 'North & South, Book 1' when I was at @NDSU.
